      "text": "This farmer and his wife were a hardworking farming couple who lived in the Earth Kingdom. Locals continually insisted the two would eventually marry, which ultimately occurred."
    },
    {
      "body": "In 100 ${link_0}, the couple encountered a sleeping ${link_1} in their storage room after the ${link_2} had escaped the ${link_3}. The farmer became frightened, attempting to ward the startled beast away with a pitchfork. His wife brought a small torch with her, which terrified Appa due to his pyrophobia. Appa subsequently destroyed the store room in his panic and flew away, leaving the couple dazed.",
